The problem seems to be capitalization: you are writing  
_gas-&gt;SpeciesIndex, when it should be _gas-&gt;speciesIndex.

The convention followed throughout Cantera is that function and method  
names always begin with a lower-case letter, and then after that new  
words are capitalized, for example &quot;getPropertyValue&quot;, not  
&quot;GetPropertyValue&quot;.  The names of constants, on the other hand, do  
begin with a capital letter (&quot;OneAtm&quot;).

Hope this solves the problem.


